Name: assign_user_story_to_sprint
Description: x_{us,sp}=1 if user story us is planned in sprint sp

Name: schedule_task_in_sprint
Description: z_{tsk,sp}=1 if task tsk is scheduled in sprint sp

Name: assign_task_to_worker
Description: y_{tsk,w}=1 if worker w executes task tsk

Name: allocate_budget_to_feature
Description: b_{f} budget allocated to feature f

Name: sprint_goal_achieved
Description: g_{sp}=1 if sprint sp achieves its goal

Name: include_feature_in_release_plan
Description: r_{f}=1 if feature f is included in the release plan

Name: sprint_utilization
Description: u_{sp} used capacity (story points) in sprint sp

Name: capacity_team_per_sprint
Description: k_{sp} selected capacity (story points) for sprint sp

Name: include_epic
Description: e_{ep}=1 if epic ep is included/active for planning

Name: stakeholder_participation_in_review
Description: m_{sr,sh}=1 if stakeholder sh participates in sprint review sr

Name: task_blocked
Description: o_{tsk}=1 if task tsk is blocked in current planning

Name: resolve_blocker
Description: rbl_{bl}=1 if blocker bl is resolved before scheduling

Name: scrumboard_card_count
Description: c_{sp} number of cards on Scrum Board for sprint sp

Name: assign_user_story_to_sprint_backlog
Description: s_{us,sbl}=1 if user story us is in sprint backlog sbl
